/>\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223305\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223305</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有無今次既事件都好，權力係會令人腐化，以前無濫權唔代表以後都唔會。<br />\n<br />\n任何既原因都唔應該成為「繞過法定守則去行使法律賦予你既特權」既基礎。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人養出黎隻狗仔率先去親身示範不守法，去示範點樣越過法例、特事特辦，後果絕對係災難性。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總有一日，朗朗乾坤，一片清明！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8c966922a46c61ad682e42b5d9723a988c7317","tid":1225722,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a273344b1b8c88b91115cefac84c7495cf7b9396","tid":1225722,"uid":37582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢點會有悔意，條氣仲唔撚順緊<br />\n明顯想搞獲野領功不成，<br />\n前幾日仲想撐落去，但共產黨派人落嚟訓示佢<br />\n死頂唔到先扮撚晒聽意見停止搞落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:44:10.000Z","msg":"唔係上面叫佢停，佢一定唔會停。"},{"pid":"a4cd81dc380db6c09c4870604326892ca0c777e2","tid":1225722,"uid":19278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1NCBu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1NCBu7.jpg&h=a47768e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e96ce8d602212740cb6af1fdccf85677d46dffb","tid":1225722,"uid":185781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T